              14 years of e-invoicing experience across India, Saudi Arabia, UAE, Malaysia, Belgium, Croatia, Poland, and Europe.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute top-[-5%] lg:top-[-22%] lg:w-126 w-full sm:w-[454px] md:w-[454px] mx-auto max-lg:md:scale-[1.2] lg:scale-0.5 inset-0 tilted-card-img-wrapper z-5"
          >
            <img
